{"word":"καί 2","slug":"καί 2","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n52017\" key=\"kai/2\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">καί νύ </orth>( <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">κε</orth>), <sense id=\"n52017.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">and now</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">κ. νύ κεν . . ἄσπετον ἤρατο κῦδος, εἰ μὴ . . </quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:373\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.373</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:8:90\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.90</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:24:50\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">24.50</biblScope> </bibl>; so <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">κ. νύ κε δή</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:17:530\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">17.530</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: also folld. by <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">εἰ</foreign> without <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μή</foreign>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:11:317\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.317</biblScope> </bibl>; by <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀλλά</foreign>, ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:630\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">630</biblScope> </bibl>: with no protasis, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">κ. νύ κεν ἐς δεκάτην γενεὴν ἕτερόν γ´ ἔτι βόσκοι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:14:325\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14.325</biblScope></bibl></cit>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}